{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_ysqcd","exhibition_name":"展览一区","location":"368,457","name":"原始青瓷鼎 ","size":"战国 通高20.5cm，口径19cm","like":43,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=75","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_ysqcd","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"鼎仿同时期青铜器造型，口沿下对称置双耳。直腹，平底，下承以外撇三足，器表施青釉。鼎最早是煮食用的陶制炊具，首见于新石器时代河南新郑裴李岗和河北武安磁山文化遗址，仰韶、龙山、屈家岭、马家滨、良渚文化等新石器时代遗址中也都有发现。商周时代的鼎多为青铜制品，并逐渐成为祭祀、征伐、丧葬等活动中陈设的一种礼器。战国至汉代出现铅釉陶和原始青瓷鼎，仿青铜器样式，多做随葬品。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/gojDdrwli_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/8Oyrl5KEh_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/8Oyrl5KEh1_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/8Oyrl5KEh2_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/8Oyrl5KEh3_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/KQy5dWWow6.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}